

=Description=

"P2P Analytics is on a mission to provide the most cutting edge analysis available, reduce defaults and maximize investor returns. P2P Analytics has recently developed a weekly distribution list based on a loan selection algorithm that promises to increase returns and greatly simplify the investing process. The algorithm assists in the selection of the lowest risk and highest return notes on the LendingClub platform based on historic data and selection factors. Along with presenting the top ranking loans, the weekly distribution comes in a simple, easy to use format that any LendingClub investor can use quickly and easily. According to company statistics, use of the algorithm can reduce default rates by up to 50 percent, greatly improving investor returns.

In addition to producing an advisory distribution, P2P Analytics also provides other forms of analysis on the rapidly growing industry of peer to peer lending. Analysis on industry trends, cash flow within the industry and indications on the future of the peer to peer lending industry are all discussed regularly on a company blog. The company plans to expand its analytical services to Prosper and Zopa in the near term future."
(http://www.virtual-strategy.com/2012/08/07/p2p-analytics-brings-cutting-edge-analysis-peer-peer-lending-investors)

